            <title><![CDATA[The Seven Deadly Sins: Origin closed beta test set for October 30 to November 5]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/the-seven-deadly-sins-origin-closed-beta-test-set-for-october-30-to-november-5</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/the-seven-deadly-sins-origin-closed-beta-test-set-for-october-30-to-november-5.1330072/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div role="main">
  
  <article>

    
<header>

  <div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Additional recruitment event currently running.</span>
      </p></div>

  

</header>  

<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p>The closed beta test for <a title="Genres > Free-to-Play [466 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/free-to-play">free-to-play</a> <a title="Genres > Open-World [748 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/open-world">open-world</a> <a title="Genres > Action RPG [1,826 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg/action-rpg">action RPG</a> <em><a title="Games > The Seven Deadly Sins: Origin [10 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/the-seven-deadly-sins-origin">The Seven Deadly Sins: Origin</a></em> will run from October 30 to November 5, publisher <a title="Companies > Netmarble [48 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/netmarble">Netmarble</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Netmarble F&amp;C [12 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/netmarble/netmarble-fc">Netmarble F&amp;C</a> <a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000002353.000007736.html" target="_blank">announced</a>. <span id="more-1001033"></span></p><p>Applications for the closed beta test ended on October 19, but Netmarble is holding an additional recruitment event through October 24, offering users another chance to join the test. Details are available on the <a href="https://7origin.netmarble.com/en/news/4/28" target="_blank">official website</a>.</p><p><em>The Seven Deadly Sins: Origin</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,639 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > PC [24,576 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3679080/The_Seven_Deadly_Sins_Origin/" target="_blank">Steam</a>, iOS, and Android on January 28, 2026.</p></div>

        
    
  </article>
