            <title><![CDATA[Wallace & Gromit in the Grand Getaway now available for PS VR2]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/wallace-gromit-in-the-grand-getaway-now-available-for-ps-vr2</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/wallace-gromit-in-the-grand-getaway-now-available-for-ps-vr2.1330057/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps-vr2">PS VR2</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Previously released for Quest headsets.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Astrea [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/atlas-v/astrea">Astrea</a> and developers <a title="Companies > Atlas V [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/atlas-v">Atlas V</a> and <a title="Companies > Albyon [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/atlas-v/albyon">Albyon</a> have released <a title="Genres > Virtual Reality [203 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/virtual-reality">virtual reality</a> <a title="Genres > Adventure [2,633 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/adventure">adventure game</a> <em><a title="Games > Wallace &amp; Gromit in the Grand Getaway [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/wallace-gromit-in-the-grand-getaway">Wallace &amp; Gromit in the Grand Getaway</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS VR2 [259 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps-vr2">PlayStation VR2</a> for $12.99. <span id="more-1000969"></span></p><p><em>Wallace &amp; Gromit in the Grand Getaway</em> first launched for Quest 2 and Quest 3 on December 7, 2023.</p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via Astrea:</p><blockquote><p><strong>About</strong></p><p>Wallace and Gromit are preparing for a well-earned golfing getaway, but mishaps and mayhem send them hurtling off course!</p><p>Step into Wallace and Gromitâs shoes and blast off on a joyful narrative VR adventure that will transport you from the warmth of West Wallaby Street to the dangers of Deep Space!</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <ul><li>Play as Wallace, Gromit, and their brand-new contraption Auto-Caddy!</li><li>Enjoy re-playable mini-games along the way.</li><li>Discover strange worlds and encounter new life forms.</li><li>Explore iconic environments in a story full of the heart and humor of a classic Aardman film.</li></ul><p>From the multi-award-winning independent animation studio Aardman (<em>Wallace &amp; Gromit</em>, <em>Chicken Run</em>, <em>Shaun the Sheep</em>) and immersive storytelling expert Atlas V (<em>Madrid Noir</em>, <em><a title="Games > Gloomy Eyes [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/gloomy-eyes">Gloomy Eyes</a></em>).</p></blockquote><p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><h2><span>PlayStation VR2 Launch Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Wallace &amp; Gromit in The Grand Getaway! I Official Trailer for PSVR2 I  Available Now" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ak67s7Kc_fA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/wallace-gromit-in-the-grand-getaway-now-available-for-ps-vr2]]></content:encoded>
